data.description: Beautiful home in a new development in west Conway! House has an open concept with vaulted ceilings, and a nice backyard with a covered patio. There are spacious guest rooms, granite throughout, and a large master closet. Wide sidewalks make for wonderful times outdoors enjoying this location and neighborhood. Home is conveniently located by many navigable Conway corridors to make commutes around town and central Arkansas easy for those coming and going.
